review: I had been to hospital and it was for general heart checkup. Consultation was fine by the doctor. Consultation fee was high, that was concern. I paid 300 extra in hospital and told practo was not updated. I would like to recommend the doctor to many people. There was less waiting time when we went. Medicines was prescribed by doctor during consultation.  Scanning, treadmill, echo test was done. Walking was suggested for 45 minutes. Doctor was friendly.
